six months. Last December it established a new general insurance subsidiary
in Indonesia in association with leading local business interests. In
January it increased its share of the New Zealand market by buying a local
subsidiary of the Guardian Royal Exchange.
Sun Alliance also has a co-operation agreement with the Japanese company,
Taisho.
