ATTEMPTS BY several shareholders of EFG, which has interests in forestry and
home and leisure products, to remove Mr Alan Joynes as chief executive was
defeated for the second time at an EGM last week, writes Michiyo Nakamoto.
Management and certain shareholders of EFG have been locked in a battle over
