Lords: Child Support Bill, third reading. Atomic Weapons Establishments
Bill, second reading.
Select committees: Environment - subject, EC draft directive on waste
landfill. Witnesses: David Trippier MP, Environment and Countryside
Minister, and officials (Room 20, 10.30am).
