<HEADLINE>
FT  13 MAY 91 / Joan of Arc festival day protests
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A French Royalist party member is arrested yesterday as he tries to lay a
wreath on Joan of Arc's statue in Paris. Marchers defied a ban to observe
the saint's festival day
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
<PAGE>
London Page 2 Photograph (Omitted).
</PAGE>
