<HEADLINE>
FT  13 MAY 91 / World News in Brief: Fans cheer Arsenal team
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Up to 200,000 fans cheered the Arsenal football team when it brought the
League Championship Trophy through the streets of north London in a victory
parade.
The team has entered the history books as the greatest champions this
century after suffering just one defeat all season.
